Package games.negative.framework.repository

Interface Repository<T>

Type Parameters:
T - The type of the entity
All Known Subinterfaces:
CommandRepository
All Known Implementing Classes:
FrameworkCommandRepository
public interface Repository<T>
Represents an object that can be stored in a repository/cache. This class provides the basic functionality of a repository.
Since:
2.1.0
Author:
Negative
